Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.66,0:00:04.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menghasilkan banyak uang\Nbelakangan ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.79,0:00:08.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi, aku beli mesin kopi yang lebih bagus\Ndan biji kopi yang lebih baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.67,0:00:12.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini sangat kaya dan harum.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.84,0:00:16.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski aku punya sinusitis\Ndan hampir tidak bisa merasakan apa pun,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.39,0:00:17.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,rasanya tetap enak.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.26,0:00:22.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gorila muda itu bilang\Ndia juga ingin mencobanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.60,0:00:23.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, kubiarkan dia mencobanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.48,0:00:30.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini panas. Kau mencoba membunuhku?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.11,0:00:32.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku.\NAku tidak tahan makanan panas.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.61,0:00:35.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebagai permintaan maaf,\Nini fosil kotoran Tyrannosaurus.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang benar saja. Siapa yang menyimpan\Nkotoran dinosaurus di antara payudara?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.70,0:00:39.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Astaga.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.41,0:00:41.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau memang ada-ada saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.83,0:00:43.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah. Kubuatkan minuman dingin lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.50,0:00:45.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau manis sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.00,0:00:48.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau pria sejati, benar-benar pujaan hati.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.50,0:00:52.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pria lebih tua modis\Ndengan pesona tak tertahankan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.97,0:00:54.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah…
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.22,0:00:56.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau membayar dana pensiun tepat waktu.\NAku bangga padamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.76,0:00:59.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sungguh tidak tahu cara memuji orang.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.81,0:01:02.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini. Aku menambahkan banyak es.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.31,0:01:03.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kelihatannya lezat.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.89,0:01:05.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan meminumnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.32,0:01:13.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang kau mau memberiku\Nserangan jantung dengan es?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.19,0:01:14.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.24,0:01:16.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pahit sekali sampai…
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.78,0:01:19.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak tahu kopi begitu pahit.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.62,0:01:21.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa kau belum bisa minum kopi hitam.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.87,0:01:23.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mau tambahkan susu?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.29,0:01:26.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini tidak apa-apa. Aku bukan anak kecil.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.42,0:01:31.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa minum kopi hitam\Ntidak menjadikanmu orang dewasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.63,0:01:34.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan membeli sesuatu.\NTolong jaga kantor.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.30,0:01:35.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.40,0:03:18.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, Pak Nagumo minum kopi\Nyang sangat pahit.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.94,0:03:22.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia mungkin berpikir\Nseleraku seperti bocah kekanak-kanakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.91,0:03:25.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa Maki juga suka kopi hitam.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.54,0:03:28.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maki sangat dewasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.66,0:03:30.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahkan selama pertukaran asisten,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.71,0:03:34.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,menurutku mereka serasi\Nsebagai orang dewasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.38,0:03:39.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini buruk. Mungkin aku tidak cocok.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.22,0:03:42.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sederhananya, kau berharap
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.09,0:03:46.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku akan membantumu terbiasa\Ndengan kopi hitam
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.68,0:03:49.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,agar Pak Nagumo berpikir kau sudah dewasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.77,0:03:51.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.52,0:03:53.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu perasaanmu, JK berwajah segar.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.98,0:03:57.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak bisa melihatmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.32,0:03:59.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak masalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.11,0:04:02.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah memikirkan 1.000 cara.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.49,0:04:04.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu aku bisa mengandalkanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.12,0:04:06.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mari kita mulai.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.49,0:04:11.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika aku melubangi kepalamu\Ndan menuangkan kopinya,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau mungkin tak akan\Nmerasakan rasa pahitnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.00,0:04:15.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selain rasa pahit,\Naku tidak akan merasakan hal lain, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.17,0:04:19.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ada cara\Nyang tidak mengacaukan penampilanku?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.13,0:04:21.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dari 1.000 cara,\N900 akan mengubah penampilanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.47,0:04:25.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika tidak, satu-satunya pilihan\Nadalah obat yang menghalangi rasa pahit.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.59,0:04:26.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu jawaban terbaik.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.01,0:04:28.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, Nona Azuha.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.56,0:04:30.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu, JK berwajah segar.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.10,0:04:34.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini sungguh memusingkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.57,0:04:43.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akhirnya aku menjadi wanita dewasa\Nyang bisa menghargai kopi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.45,0:04:47.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan menggunakan pesona dewasaku
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.70,0:04:50.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,untuk menampar Pak Nagumo!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.45,0:04:51.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Secara fisik?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.91,0:04:52.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mari kita lakukan!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.09,0:04:59.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini lezat.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Luar biasa. Sama sekali tidak pahit.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.01,0:05:04.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nona Azuha memang hebat.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.30,0:05:07.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika aku tiba-tiba bisa minum kopi,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.51,0:05:10.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pak Nagumo akan sangat terkejut.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.01,0:05:12.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.85,0:05:13.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.02,0:05:16.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pak Nagumo, aku bisa minum kopi…
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.10,0:05:20.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tersandung dan terjatuh\Ndalam perjalanan pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.82,0:05:23.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Astaga. Dia terlihat sangat tampan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.65,0:05:26.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ada sesuatu di wajahku?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.36,0:05:28.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.91,0:05:31.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, aku punya hadiah untukmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.62,0:05:33.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.54,0:05:37.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini. Aku menemukan\Nbatu berbentuk bokong ini di jalanan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.54,0:05:39.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hadiahnya sendiri payah seperti biasanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.96,0:05:42.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi entah kenapa, karena dari pria seksi,\Naku sangat bahagia.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.05,0:05:46.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perasaan apa ini? Jantungku berdebar.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.47,0:05:48.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa efek kopi memang begitu?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.01,0:05:53.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Halo?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.60,0:05:55.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,JK berwajah segar.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.35,0:05:56.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nona Azuha?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.56,0:05:58.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak sempat memberitahumu tadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.98,0:06:02.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Obat itu memiliki efek samping obat cinta.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.36,0:06:08.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pada dasarnya, itu membuatmu tertarik\Npada lawan jenis di dekatmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.41,0:06:11.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi efeknya akan segera hilang,\Njadi, jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.24,0:06:14.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo ke restoran\Ndaging panggang itu lagi kapan-kapan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.79,0:06:16.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai jumpa.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.08,0:06:22.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan mendapat masalah\Njika tak segera pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.38,0:06:26.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus menjauh dari Pak Nagumo\Nsebelum efeknya hilang.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.55,0:06:28.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika aku di sini lebih lama…
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.09,0:06:30.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mashiro, lihat.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.85,0:06:35.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat aku jatuh tadi, celanaku robek.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.89,0:06:40.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan jatuh cinta\Nkepada pria ceroboh dan tampan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.65,0:06:41.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak tahan lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.81,0:06:44.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hal konyol yang biasa dia lakukan\Nyang membuat semua orang menjauhinya
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.86,0:06:46.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,tiba-tiba sangat menggemaskan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.28,0:06:48.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau habis minum kopi?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.03,0:06:52.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau bilang itu pahit.\NKenapa tiba-tiba meminumnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.78,0:06:53.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.70,0:06:56.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,itu enak setelah aku terbiasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.16,0:06:57.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.46,0:06:59.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Luar biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.25,0:07:03.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan mengajakmu\Nke kafe favoritku lain kali.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.92,0:07:04.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini…
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.30,0:07:07.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sakit!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.30,0:07:09.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.30,0:07:11.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tiba-tiba menyentuhku,\Njadi, aku terpaksa…
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.34,0:07:14.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu sama sekali tak tampak tak sengaja.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.14,0:07:15.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sakit.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.39,0:07:17.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ada yang salah denganmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wajahmu memerah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.69,0:07:21.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, ini…
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.85,0:07:23.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau flu?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.23,0:07:27.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau demam?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.73,0:07:29.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gawat. Wajahnya terlalu dekat.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.44,0:07:32.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tetap tenang dan bersikap normal.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.12,0:07:37.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada flu yang menyebar.\NBerbaringlah dan istirahat sebentar.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.00,0:07:40.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.25,0:07:42.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa? Aku pusing.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa aku benar-benar flu?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.17,0:07:46.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan keluar sebentar.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.59,0:07:49.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mau ke mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.97,0:07:50.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.47,0:07:53.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.80,0:07:56.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tetaplah bersamaku sampai aku sembuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.39,0:07:59.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak mau sendirian lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.85,0:08:00.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mashiro?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.02,0:08:03.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, ada apa denganmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.06,0:08:06.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pak Nagumo.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.98,0:08:10.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak sadar janggut putihmu banyak\Nsampai aku sedekat ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.19,0:08:12.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak percaya kau menggodaku\Ndari jarak sedekat ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.03,0:08:14.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, lepaskan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.74,0:08:15.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.87,0:08:19.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahkan di saat seperti ini,\Nkekuatan fisikmu luar biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.00,0:08:23.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pak Nagumo, aku…
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.54,0:08:26.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,benar-benar…
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.29,0:08:28.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,suka…
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.21,0:08:29.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,suka…
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.13,0:08:30.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,suka…
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.88,0:08:33.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau terlalu dekat!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.63,0:08:35.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.64,0:08:38.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, itu yang terjadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.47,0:08:41.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak menduga efek samping seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.43,0:08:44.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku heran\Nkau tiba-tiba terlihat sangat menarik.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.10,0:08:46.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik, kau bisa bersujud di sana seharian.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.06,0:08:48.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang benar saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.32,0:08:52.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak akan mengusirmu\Nhanya karena kau tidak bisa minum kopi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.49,0:08:57.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku ingin menjadi wanita dewasa\Nyang cocok dengan kopi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.70,0:08:59.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika kau terus memperlakukanku\Nseperti anak kecil…
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.50,0:09:03.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kopi susu dengan banyak susu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.96,0:09:06.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak sengaja membuatnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kopi susu?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.88,0:09:09.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau memperlakukanku\Nseperti anak kecil lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.59,0:09:13.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mashiro, kau tidak perlu menurutiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.84,0:09:16.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lakukan saja hal-hal\Nyang tidak bisa kulakukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.80,0:09:19.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, aku tidak suka kopi susu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.31,0:09:22.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan menghargainya jika kau meminumnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.06,0:09:24.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pak Nagumo…
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.15,0:09:31.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bau.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.23,0:09:33.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pak Nagumo, susu ini sudah basi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.69,0:09:35.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf. Aku punya sinusitis,\Njadi, aku tidak tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.78,0:09:37.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berisik.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.49,0:09:43.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ikan teri kecil
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.29,0:09:47.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah basi dan berbintik-bintik
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.29,0:09:51.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya ada dua
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.17,0:09:52.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu astigmatisme?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.88,0:09:56.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, itu hanya salah diagnosis.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.72,0:10:00.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masukkan mi goreng busuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.18,0:10:02.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang kau ajarkan\Nkepada anak itu untuk dinyanyikan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.02,0:10:06.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tiba-tiba berubah menjadi Pak Nagumo
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.27,0:10:07.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau menggambarku?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.81,0:10:09.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada terlalu banyak makanan busuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.31,0:10:11.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Astaga.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.65,0:10:13.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak hilang sangat merepotkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.69,0:10:16.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serahkan saja ini kepada polisi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.86,0:10:19.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pak Nagumo, apa kau benar-benar detektif?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.24,0:10:23.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah tugas detektif\Nmembantu orang yang membutuhkan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.24,0:10:24.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sama halnya dengan polisi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.00,0:10:26.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.16,0:10:27.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Diam, Jelek.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.75,0:10:31.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa yang kau sebut jelek, Berandal?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.25,0:10:32.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau benar-benar jelek.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.84,0:10:37.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.05,0:10:39.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gadis Kecil, berapa usiamu?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.43,0:10:42.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tiga?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.35,0:10:44.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kelihatannya berapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.43,0:10:46.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak mengidap astigmatisme.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.27,0:10:51.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, itu hanya salah diagnosis
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.52,0:10:54.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak mengerti cara berpikir anak-anak.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.07,0:10:56.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.90,0:10:59.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak perlu memperdebatkan hal\Nyang tidak masuk akal.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.16,0:11:03.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau ditangkap.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.49,0:11:04.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, Gadis Kecil,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.91,0:11:06.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,bisa sebutkan namamu?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.41,0:11:09.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.04,0:11:11.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nama yang bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.50,0:11:13.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa beri tahu nama keluargamu juga?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.96,0:11:14.80,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Mereka memanggilku
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.88,0:11:16.88,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Biba.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.96,0:11:19.72,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Dia benar-benar meremehkan kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.80,0:11:22.22,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Ini sungguh pekerjaan yang sulit.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.30,0:11:25.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, di mana kau menemukannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.35,0:11:26.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di taman dekat sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.27,0:11:31.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seperti biasa, aku sedang melatih\Nteknik proteksi ciptaanku
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,lalu aku merasa sedang diawasi.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.52,0:11:35.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menoleh ke belakang…
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.19,0:11:41.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi itu tak ada hubungannya\Ndengan cerita utama,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.49,0:11:43.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi, mari kesampingkan untuk saat ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.41,0:11:46.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu, itu mungkin lebih menarik.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.04,0:11:50.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat aku hendak pergi,\Nanak ini mendatangiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.42,0:11:53.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nona Detektif, aku tersesat.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.92,0:11:55.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong bantu aku menemukan ayahku.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.50,0:12:00.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu kami pergi ke kafe\Ndan berbagi meja dengan Perdana Menteri.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.51,0:12:03.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu juga tidak berkaitan,\Njadi, kita kesampingkan juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.30,0:12:06.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cerita sampingan ini terlalu menarik.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.52,0:12:10.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo kita cari informasi.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.60,0:12:15.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.11,0:12:18.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan meminta kenalanku\Nuntuk mencari ayahnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.94,0:12:20.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.61,0:12:24.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Halo, ini Nezu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.32,0:12:25.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mencari seseorang.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.62,0:12:28.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini bukan saatnya untuk itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.58,0:12:31.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku meninggalkan organisasi\Ndan kantor pusat menggila?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.87,0:12:34.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka tahu aku bekerja sama\Ndengan wanita yang menghancurkan mereka?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.29,0:12:37.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka mengirim 1.000 pasukan\Nuntuk mengejarku?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.63,0:12:39.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahkan helikopter?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.96,0:12:42.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Boleh aku permisi sebentar?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.26,0:12:45.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Rasanya dia pergi selamanya.\N- Rasanya dia pergi selamanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.30,0:12:47.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.80,0:12:50.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, kau mencari ayah dari larva itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.68,0:12:53.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berhentilah menyebut anak manusia larva.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.35,0:12:54.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Halo.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.60,0:12:56.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau cantik sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.61,0:12:58.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau punya foto ayahmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.36,0:12:59.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.48,0:13:01.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sulit sekali menemukannya tanpa petunjuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.20,0:13:05.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berikan saja sehelai rambutnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.66,0:13:08.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau akan memakai obat aneh lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.16,0:13:11.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayolah. Lakukan saja perintahku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.79,0:13:16.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat, generator manusia buatan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.08,0:13:19.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menyuruhmu mencari seseorang,\Nbukan menciptakannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.59,0:13:21.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mencari seseorang?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.84,0:13:24.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu salah satu keahlianku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.64,0:13:30.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gadis Kecil,\Naku sama sekali tidak menakutkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.85,0:13:35.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.85,0:13:37.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia mungkin terlihat kasar,\Ntapi sangat bersih.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.86,0:13:38.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.94,0:13:41.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa aku terlihat seperti punya kuman?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Gadis Kecil.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.57,0:13:45.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa aku pernah melihatmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.99,0:13:50.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau baik-baik saja? Mau melompat sedikit\Nagar merasa lebih baik?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.58,0:13:52.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayolah.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.49,0:13:53.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak boleh begitu, Fuchan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.00,0:13:56.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski itu Asunaro,\Nkau tak boleh menendangnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.42,0:13:58.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku. Aku hanya takut.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.00,0:14:00.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, kita belum punya petunjuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.88,0:14:03.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau dipikir-pikir, kita hanya\Nmenanyai orang yang kita kenal.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.01,0:14:08.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kutunjukkan foto Fuchan\Nke orang lain dan bertanya satu per satu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.64,0:14:10.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu bisa,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.30,0:14:13.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi sebelum itu,\Naku ingin meluruskan sesuatu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.43,0:14:17.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuchan, apa niatmu sebenarnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.81,0:14:22.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mengenal Mashiro sejak awal, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.19,0:14:23.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benarkah?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.11,0:14:28.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau baru bertemu Mashiro,\Ntapi memanggilnya Nona Detektif.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.95,0:14:31.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa dia terlihat seperti detektif bagimu?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.58,0:14:33.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau menghinaku?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.91,0:14:38.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selain itu, alasanmu membungkam Asunaro\Npasti karena dia mengenalmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.34,0:14:43.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keiichiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.34,0:14:44.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mimasaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.46,0:14:46.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sedang apa kau di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.76,0:14:49.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada anak hilang.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.76,0:14:51.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuchan?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.18,0:14:53.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.10,0:14:54.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.18,0:14:56.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuchan, apa kau…
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.98,0:14:58.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menyamar.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.60,0:15:01.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau bilang dia detektif hebat,\Njadi, aku berharap banyak.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.36,0:15:02.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi dia mengecewakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.94,0:15:06.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tahu aku bukan anak hilang,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.94,0:15:10.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi dia tidak sadar\Naku putri detektif polisi.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.28,0:15:13.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal aku sudah memberikan petunjuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.45,0:15:15.99,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Mimasaka. Bibasaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.08,0:15:18.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, itu arti "Biba".
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.50,0:15:21.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Mimasaka, ada apa dengan anak ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.67,0:15:24.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuchan memang…
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.30,0:15:29.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kuduga. Tanpa saingan,\Nkau berubah menjadi pemalas.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.59,0:15:31.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ingat ini, Detektif Hebat.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.35,0:15:36.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku calon pencuri misterius legendaris,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.39,0:15:38.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pencuri Misterius Biba.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.98,0:15:41.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebagai tanda pertemuan pertama kita,\Naku mengambil ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.81,0:15:42.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dompetku!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.98,0:15:43.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai jumpa.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.02,0:15:46.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pencuri Misterius Biba menakutkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.32,0:15:48.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kejar dia, Mashiro.\NRebut kembali dompetku.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.86,0:15:51.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, isinya tanda terima dan plester.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.45,0:15:54.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mimasaka, apa yang sebenarnya\Nkau ajarkan kepada anakmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.28,0:15:56.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, aku bicara dengannya soal pekerjaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.87,0:15:59.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi akhirnya\Ndia mengidolakan pencuri misterius.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.41,0:16:00.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia cukup manis, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.79,0:16:02.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, dia manis.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.67,0:16:04.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, dia sangat manis.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.46,0:16:10.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasanya ringan sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.64,0:16:15.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.85,0:16:18.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pak Nagumo, kita dalam masalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.06,0:16:21.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kopi instannya habis.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.52,0:16:22.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hanya ada kartu ini di dalam.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.90,0:16:26.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada nasi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.69,0:16:28.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada tisu toilet.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.48,0:16:30.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Minuman kerasmu juga hilang.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.78,0:16:32.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitulah
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.91,0:16:34.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,caraku menangkap pelakunya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.32,0:16:36.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lepaskan aku! Aku akan dimakan!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.66,0:16:39.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Membobol rumah orang adalah kejahatan.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.66,0:16:40.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Diam, Jelek.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.83,0:16:43.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa yang kau sebut jelek?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.04,0:16:46.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan jadikan itu lelucon.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.54,0:16:47.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berita terkini.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.59,0:16:48.42,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Pencuri Misterius River Fake
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.50,0:16:50.46,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,mengirim pesan ke Museum Seni Tsukai,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.55,0:16:53.76,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,mengumumkan pencurian Senyum.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.84,0:16:55.80,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Itu River Fake yang legendaris.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.68,0:16:59.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, ini pencuri yang dikejar Mimasaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.72,0:17:01.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nama yang payah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.43,0:17:03.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tertulis sebagai River Fake,\Ntapi dibaca Berang-Berang.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.39,0:17:05.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini pesannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.69,0:17:08.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada banyak koreksi.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.19,0:17:13.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf memanggilmu tiba-tiba, Keiichiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.61,0:17:16.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku butuh orang berbakat.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.45,0:17:19.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, pencuri misterius itu\Nakan muncul hari ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.99,0:17:22.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rencananya selalu sempurna.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.96,0:17:24.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pencuri Misterius River Fake.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.54,0:17:26.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak ada mangsa yang pernah lolos\Nsetelah dia tandai.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.88,0:17:28.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak ada yang tahu siapa dia sebenarnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.71,0:17:33.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kali ini,\Ndia mengincar lukisan itu, Senyum.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.80,0:17:37.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lukisan ini dikatakan dilukis\Ndengan cara khusus.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.59,0:17:39.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Harganya setidaknya enam miliar yen.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.56,0:17:40.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Enam miliar?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.89,0:17:42.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika aku punya enam miliar,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.56,0:17:45.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,akan kutambahkan banyak telur rebus\Nke gyudon sampai orang muntah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.10,0:17:48.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Asistenmu benar-benar berpikir\Nseperti orang biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.65,0:17:51.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pola pikir itu ditempa\Nmelalui kerja keras sehari-hari.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.11,0:17:54.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana dengan keamanan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.82,0:17:56.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ketat sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.16,0:17:59.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada 150 petugas di dalam dan luar.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.49,0:18:03.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu jika ada yang menyentuh lukisannya,\Nbutiran besi terbang ke segala arah,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.00,0:18:06.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,air mendidih disemprotkan,\Ndan bahkan ada sengatan listrik.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.50,0:18:09.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, itu sangat berbahaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.17,0:18:12.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Melawan pria itu,\Nitu hanya permainan anak-anak.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.09,0:18:14.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau senang, bukan, Detektif Hebat?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.30,0:18:16.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya masa-masa itu\Nsudah lama berlalu,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.34,0:18:17.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pak Kepala.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.68,0:18:22.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bersamamu seperti ini\Nmengingatkanku pada hari itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.39,0:18:24.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini membangkitkan kenangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.85,0:18:27.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah hari itu juga bulan purnama?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.94,0:18:29.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Salju turun, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.69,0:18:30.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benarkah?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.61,0:18:32.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau memakai jaket hitam.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.11,0:18:33.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, warnanya hijau.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.65,0:18:37.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Ingatanku buram seiring makin tua.\N- Ingatanku buram seiring makin tua.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.95,0:18:40.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayolah. Sadarlah, kalian berdua.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.99,0:18:43.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah hampir waktunya\Nuntuk kejahatan yang diperingatkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.79,0:18:46.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia bisa datang kapan saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.08,0:18:48.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mati lampu?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.21,0:18:49.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nyalakan kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.42,0:18:50.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mashiro, senter.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.75,0:18:51.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.92,0:18:55.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, lihat.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.01,0:18:57.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lukisannya hilang.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.88,0:19:00.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu River Fake?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.01,0:19:03.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mashiro, bersiaplah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.43,0:19:04.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.35,0:19:06.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau akan berburu pterosaurus?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.18,0:19:07.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada orang di jendela.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.64,0:19:10.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu River Fake!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.15,0:19:12.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Halo, Semuanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.31,0:19:14.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pertama, aku ingin mengatakan sesuatu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.40,0:19:17.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah sistem keamanan\Nhari ini terlalu ketat?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.74,0:19:18.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berhasil.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.28,0:19:24.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak percaya kita menggunakan\Nwewenang pemerintah padanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.70,0:19:27.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, ada yang ingin kutanyakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.54,0:19:32.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini buruk! Semuanya, tiarap!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.50,0:19:34.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Granat sinar?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.50,0:19:37.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mashiro, kau bisa melihat?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.09,0:19:38.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hampir tidak bisa.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.72,0:19:39.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di mana River Fake?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.80,0:19:41.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Coba kulihat.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.51,0:19:45.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia di lantai, dibutakan oleh cahaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.14,0:19:47.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, seharusnya kau lebih berhati-hati.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.47,0:19:49.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau serangga\Nyang mati karena kentut sendiri?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.81,0:19:51.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia kabur!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.98,0:19:58.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Senyum adalah milikku!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.49,0:20:01.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, aku akan memakai\Nbuatan khusus Nona Azuha…
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.74,0:20:02.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkinkah…
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.74,0:20:05.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Arloji penyembur api.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.28,0:20:07.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang ada yang lebih kejam\Ndaripada aslinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.41,0:20:10.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, Mashiro, lukisannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.29,0:20:11.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika kau menggunakan api,\Nitu akan terbakar.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.04,0:20:13.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.17,0:20:15.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah memeriksa latar belakang Senyum.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.25,0:20:18.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lukisan itu dibuat\Ndengan kain tahan api khusus.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.05,0:20:21.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu telah bertahan\Ndalam banyak perang sejauh ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.76,0:20:24.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu sebabnya nilainya enam miliar.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.10,0:20:27.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, api sebesar ini bisa dengan mudah…
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.39,0:20:30.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu bisa dengan mudah\Nmengubah lukisan menjadi abu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.39,0:20:32.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mungkin.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.35,0:20:35.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang akan kau lakukan?\NHarganya enam miliar.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.15,0:20:38.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bisa menambahkan telur rebus\Nke gyudon-ku lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.78,0:20:41.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau berencana membayar utang\Ndengan uang yang ditabung untuk telur?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.40,0:20:42.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.95,0:20:45.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mustahil kita memajang karya seni aslinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.54,0:20:50.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mimasaka, kau sangat kompeten.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.66,0:20:53.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, di mana pencurinya?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.25,0:20:56.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah…
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.00,0:20:59.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.05,0:21:03.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia mengeluarkan gas\Nuntuk membuat semua orang pingsan.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.89,0:21:07.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.10,0:21:08.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sesuatu yang mudah terbakar\Nsedang bergerak.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.01,0:21:11.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia terlihat seperti pria tua yang lusuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.31,0:21:14.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial. Seperti yang kuharapkan\Ndari River Fake.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.61,0:21:20.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuchan, kau mengikuti kami?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.90,0:21:22.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagus, Fuchan.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.32,0:21:23.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.70,0:21:26.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kukira kau mengagumi pencuri misterius itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.20,0:21:29.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mungkin.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.70,0:21:30.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.08,0:21:33.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mungkin River Fake yang kukagumi
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.79,0:21:37.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,adalah pria tua berantakan ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.79,0:21:39.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.76,0:21:44.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pak Nagumo, ini dari Pak Mimasaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.76,0:21:46.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.89,0:21:50.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia berterima kasih karena kau\Nmembantu penangkapan River Fake.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.43,0:21:53.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu menjijikkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.35,0:21:55.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seleranya dalam suvenir sangat buruk.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.69,0:22:00.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Fuchan.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.23,0:22:02.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu suvenirku untuk Keiichiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.48,0:22:04.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nagumo Keiichiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.53,0:22:06.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku membantumu kali ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.91,0:22:08.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi aku akan mengalahkanmu lain kali.
